条不紊的复习。而我自己都在徘徊迷茫之中度过，心里真的很难受。学不下去时，去看着书里的鸡汤，感觉又充满了希望和动力。合上书，面对现实时，却又手足无措。 知道自己不能再这样下去了，我已经荒废了很多学业，虚度了太多的光阴，我还有无数个梦想等着自己去实现。一摸即将来临，高考已经走进。现在不管是我的学业，还是心理都有问题，我该怎么办？"},"attached_info":"CkAIhbzh5qPHyf1GEAMaCDc4MjEwNzA2IMCqtpEGMAA4ekAvaAByCTUyMTY3OTk1MHgAqgEJYmlsbGJvYXJk0gEA","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"48_1647218313.097198","card_id":"Q_521695013","target":{"id":521695013,"title":"本人是一名高中生，初中开始看小说，然后就看上瘾了，中考前一天晚上还在看，现在也是，请问怎么戒掉？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/521695013","type":"question","created":1647159607,"answer_count":168,"follower_count":204,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[73,10576],"comment_count":5,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkEIhbzh5qPHyf1GEAMaCDc4MjE0MDE3ILfStpEGMAU4zAFAMGgAcgk1MjE2OTUwMTN4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]},{"type":"hot_list_feed","style_type":"1","id":"49_1647218313.0975869","card_id":"Q_389671184","target":{"id":389671184,"title":"有没有好看的校园小甜文，要求就是越甜越好，我不怕得糖尿病？","url":"https://api.zhihu.com/questions/389671184","type":"question","created":1587515319,"answer_count":362,"follower_count":967,"author":{"type":"people","user_type":"people","id":"0","url_token":"","url":"","name":"用户","headline":"","avatar_url":"https://pica.zhimg.com/aadd7b895_s.jpg"},"bound_topic_ids":[4105,9162,718581,782268],"comment_count":0,"is_following":false,"excerpt":""},"attached_info":"CkEIhbzh5qPHyf1GEAMaCDQ4ODcxOTEyILef/vQFMAA4xwdAMWgAcgkzODk2NzExODR4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA==","detail_text":"27 万热度","trend":0,"debut":false,"children":[{"type":"answer","thumbnail":""}]}],"description":{"time":"2022-03-14 08:38:33"}}